a><ul class='ez-toc-list-level-3' ><li class='ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-9\" href=\"#\" data-href=\"https:\/\/www.noiise.com\/ressources\/creation-site-internet\/plugins-wordpress-leurs-avantages-et-les-inconvenients\/#Vulnerabilite_de_votre_site_accrue\" >Vuln\u00e9rabilit\u00e9 de votre site accrue<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-10\" href=\"#\" data-href=\"https:\/\/www.noiise.com\/ressources\/creation-site-internet\/plugins-wordpress-leurs-avantages-et-les-inconvenients\/#Impossibilite_de_repondre_a_des_demandes_specifiques\" >Impossibilit\u00e9 de r\u00e9pondre \u00e0 des demandes sp\u00e9cifiques<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-11\" href=\"#\" data-href=\"https:\/\/www.noiise.com\/ressources\/creation-site-internet\/plugins-wordpress-leurs-avantages-et-les-inconvenients\/#Conflit_et_dysfonctionnement_entre_les_plugins\" >Conflit et dysfonctionnement entre les plugins<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-12\" href=\"#\" data-href=\"https:\/\/www.noiise.com\/ressources\/creation-site-internet\/plugins-wordpress-leurs-avantages-et-les-inconvenients\/#Reduction_de_la_vitesse_de_chargement_du_site\" >R\u00e9duction de la vitesse de chargement du site<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-13\" href=\"#\" data-href=\"https:\/\/www.noiise.com\/ressources\/creation-site-internet\/plugins-wordpress-leurs-avantages-et-les-inconvenients\/#Comment_choisir_un_plugin_WordPress\" >Comment choisir un plugin WordPress ?<\/a><ul class='ez-toc-list-level-3' ><li class='ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-14\" href=\"#\" data-href=\"https:\/\/www.noiise.com\/ressources\/creation-site-internet\/plugins-wordpress-leurs-avantages-et-les-inconvenients\/#Prendre_le_temp